collectionMetadata.name: National Library Singapore Digitised Images
collectionMetadata.description:
This dataset is a list of images digitised from the collections of the National Library of Singapore and our partners. 

These materials cover a collection of photographs and artworks related to Singapore.

For enquiries, please email ref@nlb.gov.sg
